      <data key="d1">"The Chain symbolizes the burdens of Marley's past life, constructed from various items representing greed and constraint."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Chain symbolizes the consequences of Jacob Marley's earthly actions, representing guilt, regret, and the burdens carried through life and after death."</data>
