      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Jacob Marley is Scrooge's deceased former business partner who returns as a ghost to warn Scrooge of his impending fate."&lt;SEP&gt;"Marley is Scrooge's deceased business partner, whose death is emphasized as pivotal to the story, representing themes of regret and mortality."&lt;SEP&gt;"Marley is Scrooge's deceased partner, whose ghostly figure appears to warn Scrooge about the consequences of his actions and attitudes."</data>
