    </node>
    <node id="&quot;FRED&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Fred is Scrooge's cheerful nephew who embodies the holiday spirit and the importance of family connections."&lt;SEP&gt;"Fred is Scrooge's nephew who expresses admiration for Scrooge, suggesting a close familial relationship despite Scrooge's former coldness."&lt;SEP&gt;"Fred is Scrooge's nephew who hosts a Christmas gathering, indicating familial connections and the theme of family during the holiday season."&lt;SEP&gt;"Fred is Scrooge's nephew, who expresses warmth and surprise during Scrooge's visit to Christmas dinner, embodying familial love and connection."&lt;SEP&gt;"Fred is Scrooge's nephew, who invites Scrooge to dinner, representing familial love and the spirit of generosity which contrasts Scrooge's coldness."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-e7637ff18c5ded77a68cce0a87883fad&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-89777b838d5447c7bd1ec11282c4ee89&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9e3921da66da5d761ab73cd849af6c43&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-19fcf3bed0b4df750efc07831690f550&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8f738cb25d60a7dab782162d9d0a25ed</data>
    </node>
