      <data key="d1">"The Bundle is a collection of stolen items that characters discuss and appraise, representing the group's shared illicit activities."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Bundle refers to the possessions belonging to the deceased man, including personal items being discussed and evaluated by Joe and the Woman."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-e1f29eeadc1d8ab46dc8a0bbd3c56b64&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-60fc063c79fc0d4acc91a57e79de04dc</data>
