    </node>
    <node id="&quot;TOPPER&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Topper is a character who engages in playful banter during a family gathering, displaying a humorous and lighthearted personality."&lt;SEP&gt;"Topper is a character who engages in playful interactions during the celebration, notably in the game of blind man's-buff."&lt;SEP&gt;"Topper is another character who attends the Christmas gathering, representing camaraderie and the warmth of friendship during the festive occasion."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-773d0df1dd25c356f7b771d780583e09&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-43c9bee23adfa77aa9dedd22401bba7d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-19fcf3bed0b4df750efc07831690f550</data>
    </node>
