      <data key="d1">"The Beacon of Hope symbolizes the guiding light that leads Scrooge toward a more fulfilled existence."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9c43dac2fcd5b578242d907ea6f8fc7b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE CHANGING TIDES OF EXISTENCE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Changing Tides of Existence signify how life continually evolves and shifts based on our choices."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9c43dac2fcd5b578242d907ea6f8fc7b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;FEZZIWIG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Fezziwig is a character known for hosting a domestic ball, demonstrating the ability to make others happy and contributing to the joyful atmosphere of the event."&lt;SEP&gt;"Fezziwig is a character who exemplifies joy and celebration, particularly during Christmas gatherings with his wife and guests."&lt;SEP&gt;"Fezziwig is a jovial character from Scrooge's past who represents a positive influence and joyful memories of Scrooge's apprenticeship."&lt;SEP&gt;"Fezziwig is a jovial figure who embodies festive spirit, known for his lively celebrations and influence over Scrooge and others during Christmas Eve."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-89777b838d5447c7bd1ec11282c4ee89&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b2f98bc7abb0c67d4c86055c7fd72218&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8bc1edd983869352d14cf0886a9175a7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c6c248858d1b13ab7ee9ca13c1aeed6b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;DINNER-CARRIERS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Dinner-carriers are individuals depicted as bringing their meals to bakers' shops, highlighting the community's preparation for festive meals."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-b0f459f5af1c3a5e0b92cbe4ee48b77b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;JUDGMENT ON HIM&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Judgment on Him refers to the collective judgment made about the deceased character whose belongings are being appraised, highlighting morality in the context of theft."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-60fc063c79fc0d4acc91a57e79de04dc</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;FIRE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Fire represents warmth and comfort, contrasting with Scrooge's experiences and illustrating the festive spirit brought by the Ghost."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-843b5b2f944c7413d9ca876e2e2f151f</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;GHOST OF CHRISTMAS FUTURE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Ghost of Christmas Future signifies the potential consequences of Scrooge's life choices if they remain unchanged."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9c43dac2fcd5b578242d907ea6f8fc7b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE UMBRELLA OF PROTECTION&quot;">
