      <data key="d1">"The Arena of Transformation reflects Scrooge's journey toward becoming a more compassionate and caring individual."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9c43dac2fcd5b578242d907ea6f8fc7b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE EMBERS OF NEW BEGINNINGS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Embers of New Beginnings highlight the moments when Scrooge makes choices leading to transformation."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9c43dac2fcd5b578242d907ea6f8fc7b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MEAT&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CATEGORY"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Meat is among the lavish food items presented by the Ghost, emphasizing the opulence and communal spirit of festive meals."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-843b5b2f944c7413d9ca876e2e2f151f</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MRS. FEZZIWIG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Mrs. Fezziwig is Fezziwig's partner in the domestic ball, engaging with guests and promoting a warm, festive environment."&lt;SEP&gt;"Mrs. Fezziwig is Fezziwig's wife, participating in the joyous celebration and embodying the spirit of Christmas joy alongside her husband."&lt;SEP&gt;"Mrs. Fezziwig is the wife of Fezziwig, participating in the celebrations and dances, showcasing joy and hospitality during the festive season."&lt;SEP&gt;"Mrs. Fezziwig is the wife of Mr. Fezziwig, embodying the spirit of generosity and community celebration during Christmas."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-89777b838d5447c7bd1ec11282c4ee89&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b2f98bc7abb0c67d4c86055c7fd72218&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8bc1edd983869352d14cf0886a9175a7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9e3921da66da5d761ab73cd849af6c43</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE TOWNSPEOPLE&quot;">
