      <data key="d1">"Sucking-Pigs are another item depicted in the Ghost's feast, representing the richness of Christmas celebrations and feasts."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-843b5b2f944c7413d9ca876e2e2f151f</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE GHOST OF CHRISTMAS PAST&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Ghost of Christmas Past is a spirit who shows Scrooge scenes from his history to evoke remorse and drive change."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Ghost of Christmas Past is an apparition that guides Scrooge through memories, helping him to revisit significant moments from his early life."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-90b95db5c53e4364a6bee36b7aa4d70f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b2f98bc7abb0c67d4c86055c7fd72218</data>
