      <data key="d2">chunk-9c43dac2fcd5b578242d907ea6f8fc7b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE GIFT OF EMPATHY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Gift of Empathy represents the ability to connect deeply with others that Scrooge begins to cultivate."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9c43dac2fcd5b578242d907ea6f8fc7b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE BOND OF BELONGING&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Bond of Belonging illustrates the connections we create that fulfill our need for community and acceptance."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9c43dac2fcd5b578242d907ea6f8fc7b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;GRAVE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Grave represents Scrooge's feared future if he continues on his current path, serving as a pivotal point in his realization and transformation."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-91572b3cd42786ba4cb2f180ca25cbf4</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE DOMESTIC BALL&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Domestic Ball is a festive gathering hosted by Fezziwig that fosters joy and celebration among the guests."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-b2f98bc7abb0c67d4c86055c7fd72218</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;FIFTEEN 'BOB'">
      <data key="d0">"CATEGORY"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Fifteen 'Bob' refers to the weekly income of Bob Cratchit, signifying the family's financial struggles."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-b0f459f5af1c3a5e0b92cbe4ee48b77b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;OLD BONES&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Old Bones symbolize the remnants of past lives and serve as a metaphor for mortality and the possessions left behind after death."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-60fc063c79fc0d4acc91a57e79de04dc</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE HEAVY DARKNESS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Heavy Darkness represents the oppressive nature of Scrooge's emotional state and his fears."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9c43dac2fcd5b578242d907ea6f8fc7b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE CHORUS OF REGRETS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Chorus of Regrets represents the amalgamation of sorrowful reflections that shape Scrooge’s current state."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9c43dac2fcd5b578242d907ea6f8fc7b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE BRIDGE TO UNDERSTANDING&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
