      <data key="d1">"The Healing Power of Compassion signifies the transformative effects kindness has on individuals and their relationships."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9c43dac2fcd5b578242d907ea6f8fc7b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MR. SCROOGE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Mr. Scrooge is Bob Cratchit's employer, who demonstrates kindness towards the Cratchit family, especially regarding Tiny Tim's situation."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-1d4b58de5429cd1261370c231c8673e8</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;TIM CRATCHIT&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
