    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE SHOP&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Shop is a dingy place where various items like old rags, iron, and scraps are bought and sold, representing decline and neglect."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Shop is where Old Joe conducts his business, dealing in assorted wares and stolen items, providing a setting for the interactions of the characters."</data>
