      <data key="d1">"Christmas-time is depicted as a significant period in the narrative, evoking themes of warmth, family, and reflection."&lt;SEP&gt;"Christmas-time represents a seasonal context wherein the conversations and events are taking place, contrasting with the themes of neglect and moral introspection."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-c6c248858d1b13ab7ee9ca13c1aeed6b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f1a4fbcf1ed86864b9bfd5e8dba4c683</data>
