    <node id="&quot;SCROOGE'S NEPHEW&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Scrooge's Nephew is a character known for his laughter and positive disposition, contrasting with his Uncle Scrooge's miserly attitude."&lt;SEP&gt;"Scrooge's Nephew is a cheerful character who values Christmas and pleads with Scrooge to embrace its spirit."&lt;SEP&gt;"Scrooge's Nephew is cheerful and embodies the spirit of Christmas, attempting to bring joy and cheer to Scrooge despite his uncle's negativity."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-773d0df1dd25c356f7b771d780583e09&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5dac41b3f9eeaf794f0147400b1718cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-74e2466de2f67fd710ef2f20c0a8d9e0</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;ALI BABA&quot;">
