      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Christmas Toys and Presents symbolize celebration, family joy and the innocence of childhood during festive times."&lt;SEP&gt;"Christmas toys and presents represent the joyous and giving nature of the Christmas season, contributing to the festive atmosphere described."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-54bdd22db1f84a965b5f4c06c9216d8d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-89777b838d5447c7bd1ec11282c4ee89</data>
