      <data key="d1">"The Haunting Echoes represent the lasting impacts of Scrooge's actions reverberating in his life."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9c43dac2fcd5b578242d907ea6f8fc7b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE VALUE OF COMPASSION&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Value of Compassion highlights the importance of kindness and empathy in transforming Scrooge's life."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9c43dac2fcd5b578242d907ea6f8fc7b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE TIDES OF SPIRIT&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Tides of Spirit reflect the ebb and flow of emotions and experiences as Scrooge transitions in his journey."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9c43dac2fcd5b578242d907ea6f8fc7b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MEMORIES&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Memories serve as a crucial theme in the narrative, representing the power of the past to influence the present."</data>
