    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE MANSION&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Mansion is a dilapidated structure associated with Scrooge's past, reflecting his history and upbringing."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-8590d9263cd2cd4fa583c432fc54e6c3</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE MAN WHOSE DEATH CAUSED REFLECTION&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The man whose death is central to Scrooge's reflections and the emotions of those around him, prompting discussions about life and loss."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-83ac129dc9b56f84c46760d153d68e93</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE DANCE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Dance is a central activity during the Christmas Eve celebration, highlighting joy, community, and the festive atmosphere fostered by characters like Fezziwig and his family."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-8bc1edd983869352d14cf0886a9175a7</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;SCROOGE'S TRANSFORMATION&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Scrooge's Transformation is the culmination of his experiences with the spirits leading to a change of heart."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9c43dac2fcd5b578242d907ea6f8fc7b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE RADIANCE OF HUMANITY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Radiance of Humanity illustrates the positive aspects of connection that Scrooge learns to embrace."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9c43dac2fcd5b578242d907ea6f8fc7b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE LAYERS OF UNDERSTANDING&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Layers of Understanding capture the complexities of growth and realizations that Scrooge experiences."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9c43dac2fcd5b578242d907ea6f8fc7b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE CLERK&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Clerk is Scrooge's employee who works in a small, cold office and tries to keep warm in a challenging work environment under Scrooge's miserly oversight."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Clerk works for Scrooge and displays more warmth and cheerfulness, representing the typical view of Christmas."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-5dac41b3f9eeaf794f0147400b1718cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-74e2466de2f67fd710ef2f20c0a8d9e0</data>
