    <node id="&quot;THE PARROT&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Parrot is introduced in Scrooge's recollections, showcasing his whimsical childhood imagination and past adventures."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-8590d9263cd2cd4fa583c432fc54e6c3</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE CREDITOR&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The creditor is a figure whose impending death brings both worry and a sense of relief to the Cratchit family, as they rely on his decisions for their financial future."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-83ac129dc9b56f84c46760d153d68e93</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE COOK&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Cook is a character who is part of the staff at Fezziwig's establishment, contributing to the festive atmosphere during the Christmas Eve celebration."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-8bc1edd983869352d14cf0886a9175a7</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE SHADOWS OF THE PAST&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Shadows of the Past reflect the lingering presence of former decisions in shaping Scrooge's current reality."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9c43dac2fcd5b578242d907ea6f8fc7b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE CHAIN REACTION OF CHANGE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Chain Reaction of Change signifies how Scrooge’s transformation can inspire others toward their journeys."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9c43dac2fcd5b578242d907ea6f8fc7b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE WEDDING OF HEART AND MIND&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Wedding of Heart and Mind symbolizes the alignment of Scrooge's beliefs with his newfound compassionate actions."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9c43dac2fcd5b578242d907ea6f8fc7b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;SWEEPING CHANGES&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Sweeping Changes indicate the larger themes within the narrative regarding the need for transformation in moral attitudes and behaviors around Christmas."</data>
