    <node id="&quot;THE GHOST&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Ghost is a supernatural entity guiding Scrooge through his memories and past experiences relevant to Christmas."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Ghost refers to a supernatural entity that provides moral lessons to Scrooge, highlighting themes of compassion and social responsibility through its interactions with him."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Ghost represents a supernatural being guiding Scrooge through reflections on death and its emotional implications for the living."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Ghost represents the apparitional spirit of Jacob Marley, who conveys the message of moral responsibility and the consequences of a life without compassion."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Ghost represents the spectral apparition of Jacob Marley, who has returned to communicate with Scrooge."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Ghost serves as a supernatural entity representing memory and conscience, forcing Scrooge to confront his past choices."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Ghost serves as a supernatural guide for Scrooge, prompting him to reflect on his life and choices."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Ghost symbolizes the spirit of Christmas, embodying generosity, joy, and mirth."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-54bdd22db1f84a965b5f4c06c9216d8d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-503f0bfa5453467c7c61d160a3540eca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-19d72c57ae3408758b18d2568e86dc6b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8590d9263cd2cd4fa583c432fc54e6c3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-359187e7571bda4b0b08b2e0b6581e52&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c6c248858d1b13ab7ee9ca13c1aeed6b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1aa50206d02ed89418f65f97c6441d1c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-83ac129dc9b56f84c46760d153d68e93</data>
    </node>
