    <edge source="&quot;CHRISTMAS&quot;" target="&quot;SCROOGE&quot;">
      <data key="d3">110.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Scrooge expresses disdain for Christmas, viewing it negatively, which contrasts with its intended spirit of joy and generosity."&lt;SEP&gt;"Scrooge is an integral character experiencing a moment of realization within the context of Christmas festivities."&lt;SEP&gt;"Scrooge views Christmas negatively, seeing it as a time for financial burdens, in stark contrast to its positive connotations."&lt;SEP&gt;"Scrooge's character is a direct juxtaposition to the festive spirit of Christmas, as he is depicted as a miser who resents the holiday."&lt;SEP&gt;"Scrooge's disdain for Christmas is evident as he refuses to embrace the spirit of giving that the holiday represents."&lt;SEP&gt;"Scrooge's feelings towards Christmas contrast sharply with the joyous memories and interactions he revisits due to the ghost's guidance."&lt;SEP&gt;"Scrooge's memories are closely tied to the theme of Christmas, reflecting both sorrow and nostalgic joy."&lt;SEP&gt;"Scrooge's reflections on Christmas are pivotal to his character development and path towards redemption."&lt;SEP&gt;"Scrooge's transformation leads him to embrace the spirit of Christmas, which symbolizes redemption and change for him."&lt;SEP&gt;"Scrooge's transformation throughout the Christmas event signifies a deeper connection to the holiday's true meaning."&lt;SEP&gt;"Scrooge's ultimate acceptance of Christmas represents his full transformation and commitment to living a better life."&lt;SEP&gt;"The celebration of Christmas evokes feelings of joy and familial affection that contrast Scrooge's earlier demeanor, highlighting his character arc."</data>
      <data key="d5">"acceptance, transformation"&lt;SEP&gt;"contrast, character arc"&lt;SEP&gt;"cynicism, seasonal celebration"&lt;SEP&gt;"holiday spirit, contrast"&lt;SEP&gt;"holiday spirit, opposition"&lt;SEP&gt;"negativity, holiday spirit"&lt;SEP&gt;"nostalgia, holiday significance"&lt;SEP&gt;"nostalgia, transformation"&lt;SEP&gt;"redemption, reflection"&lt;SEP&gt;"redemption, transformation"&lt;SEP&gt;"transformation, holiday significance"&lt;SEP&gt;"transformation, holiday spirit"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-90d5764e301321c087f5a8f78b73a145&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5dac41b3f9eeaf794f0147400b1718cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-89777b838d5447c7bd1ec11282c4ee89&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8590d9263cd2cd4fa583c432fc54e6c3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-91572b3cd42786ba4cb2f180ca25cbf4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bb21d58d36c6306fd8810ddd51c4a971&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-99b0ec7f7e006561352b5d65e849611d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-da2472b4ef2a535b62908f14d0fb0ca9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-74e2466de2f67fd710ef2f20c0a8d9e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-91614df5cb74cbe5e109a338a82041e9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8f738cb25d60a7dab782162d9d0a25ed</data>
    </edge>
