    <edge source="&quot;SCROOGE'S NEPHEW&quot;" target="&quot;SCROOGE&quot;">
      <data key="d3">24.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Scrooge's Nephew is trying to engage Scrooge in the spirit of Christmas, showcasing a conflict between differing views on the holiday."&lt;SEP&gt;"Scrooge's Nephew often expresses pity for Scrooge, contrasting his lighthearted demeanor with Scrooge's miserliness."&lt;SEP&gt;"Scrooge's Nephew tries to spread Christmas cheer to Scrooge, who continually rebuffs him, showcasing their contrasting attitudes toward the holiday."</data>
